|----------|--------|-------------|---------|
| **Core** | **Kernel Overhead** | **8.37 Âµs / node** | ðŸš€ 10x Faster than Frameworks |
| **Core** | **Tool Chaining** | **0.45 ms (Total)** | âš¡ Instant |
| **Core** | **Determinism** | **Byte-for-Byte Match** | âœ… Exact Replay |
| **Core** | **Parallelism** | **206ms (4x 200ms)** | ðŸ§µ True Parallel Fan-out |
| **Throughput** | **Node Throughput** | **720,000+ nodes/sec** | High Frequency |
| **Latency** | **Task Dispatch** | ~1.4 Âµs | Real-time |
| **Latency** | **Policy Check** | ~3.0 Âµs | Zero-Cost Security |
